{"tid":2174351,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再食Carbone","createTime":"2020-08-26T00:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T03:29:13.000Z","uid":226902,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8e16a34140c7e9f1dda23b19263b0e1ba5a606d1","tid":2174351,"uid":226902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:15:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>葉劉70歲生日去呢間 店主邀請影相送蛋糕 最出名長通粉</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://etw-image.nextdigital.com.hk/images/e-paper/20200825/large/1598344369_b806.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw-image.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200825%2Flarge%2F1598344369_b806.jpg&h=a8852667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天葉劉淑儀慶祝70歲生日，在自己專頁表示去了一間餐廳慶祝，雖然因晚市禁堂食，她只是到餐廳切蛋糕，但相信不少人都想知道她去了哪間餐廳。原來是中環的美式意菜館Carbone﹗餐廳創辦人是Mario Carbone，一手復興美式意菜，在紐約很有名氣，2013年甫開業，已獲紐約米芝蓮評為1星餐廳，至今不變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">擺明當你班人無到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4faf51e478cdc92586aedb369e69767d1f4a3811","tid":2174351,"uid":89046,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:41:57.000Z","msg":"70歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e3b3bc86bfda1a04eab542b86f2068d388f190","tid":2174351,"uid":55851,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:50:18.000Z","msg":"葉劉又使出死亡之吻"},{"pid":"d30a55000365b9f98160a7a57406751eac517499","tid":2174351,"uid":193138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4faf51e478cdc92586aedb369e69767d1f4a3811","tid":2174351,"uid":89046,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:41:57.000Z","msg":"70歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"吸精大法<br />\n吸乾左佢老公自己咪咁長命"},{"pid":"c3097cf8c9f6f826217a0d9d4a0f00d96afeb3c2","tid":2174351,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"